In a promotional clip of their reality show Chad Loves Michelle, the real character of Chad has been revealed in a show which is supposed to follow them through until they say I do. Michelle who has been open about her depression and her treatment in a mental health centre was allegedly mocked by Chad after she brought up the issue about race. “I said something to him on the lines of ‘Well, Chad, because you are not Black you would not understand why I communicate the way I do. Maybe because you didn’t grow up around a lot of Black people.’ So that was very, very offensive to Chad…. And this is not to justify it, but yesterday when we had the disagreement, he said ‘Did you take your meds today?”, she told their therapist. Take a look below: 